      </div>
      <div class="cards-grid" style="margin-top: 40px; max-width: 960px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;">
        <div class="card reveal">
          <div class="card__body">
            <h3>1. Full Property Inspection</h3>
            <p style="color:var(--gray);">A licensed Wernex technician inspects the full interior and exterior of your home — foundation walls, crawl spaces, attics, garage, and all wood-to-soil contact points. We use moisture meters and probing tools to check areas where termites are most likely to be active.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="card reveal">
          <div class="card__body">
            <h3>2. Detailed Report &amp; Recommendation</h3>
            <p style="color:var(--gray);">After the inspection, you receive a written report with findings, photos of any activity or damage, and a clear treatment recommendation. For WDI reports, we follow NPMA-33 standards required by lenders. No pressure, no upselling — just honest assessment.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="card reveal">
          <div class="card__body">
            <h3>3. Treatment &amp; Warranty</h3>
            <p style="color:var(--gray);">If treatment is needed, we schedule at your convenience — often within 48 hours. Liquid barrier treatments are completed in a single visit. Every treatment includes a damage warranty and follow-up monitoring to ensure the colony is fully eliminated.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ═══ TESTIMONIAL ═══ -->
